OL,6,FA funeral directors in is currently
OL,7,Fbeing investigated by police with a
OL,8,Ffocus on fraud offences.
OL,10,F(TVP) said it was made aware of
OL,11,Fconcerns relating to the business
OL,12,Fpractices of R&H Barker Funeral
OL,13,FDirectors on Wednesday 10 April.
OL,15,FThe force then carried out a number of
OL,16,Fimmediate enquiries, and two warrants
OL,17,Fwere carried out at premises connected
OL,18,Fwith the business in Harcourt Road,
OL,19,FWantage and Wantage Road, Didcot on
OL,20,FSunday 14 April.
