OL,3,COxfordshire funeral directors being
OL,4,Cinvestigated by police
OL,6,FTVP are now working together with
OL,7,Fpartners including Environmental
OL,8,FHealth, to investigate business
OL,9,Fpractices at the sites.
OL,11,FThe force said its "focus is on fraud
OL,12,Foffences and one offence of prevention
OL,13,Fof a lawful and decent burial".
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "At this stage of
OL,16,Fthe investigation we have found no
OL,17,Fevidence of any criminal offence and
OL,18,Fno arrests have been made.
