OL,6,F"We know this will be of concern to
OL,7,Ffamilies and individuals who have used
OL,8,Fthis business however we can confirm
OL,9,Four enquiries into the prevention of a
OL,10,Flawful and decent burial relates to
OL,11,Fone individual only, and we are
OL,12,Fworking to contact their next of kin.
OL,14,F"We do not believe that any other
OL,15,Ffamilies are impacted."
OL,17,FThe funeral directors are closed
OL,18,Fwhilst the investigation is ongoing.
